name: Sophia Katherine
description: I am looking for the one who will rule every way that I move, who will be by my side. Real friend, real lover, soul so native and close to mine. I want to be your woman if you are not afraid of your desires and your dreams. When you want to hear and understand. When even with doubts you continue going further. If I can believe your words as it is the same you do. I like differences so I do not expect us enjoy the same things, I want us staying ourselves with feeling of respect and desire with vision.
